{"tid":984553,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人話我知應該點做。。","createTime":"2019-01-17T01:50:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-17T05:12:53.000Z","uid":89493,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4ef6a05caf22a8715a51732cdd016d15009b27dc","tid":984553,"uid":89493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T01:50:45.000Z","msg":"我男朋友同我一齊左五六年之後分開左兩年左右，<br />\n<br />\n分開左既時候佢間中都會搵我約我！<br />\n<br />\n最近一齊番年幾，係今日我偷睇左佢電話，<br />\n<br />\n我知好唔應該，<br />\n<br />\n但睇完我發現原來係我地分開個段時間佢有拍拖，<br />\n<br />\n我同佢一齊番個陣有問過佢有無第個，<br />\n<br />\n佢話無，所以我當我諗多左，<br />\n<br />\n但原來我睇佢電話發現我同佢一齊番個陣，<br />\n<br />\n佢同我講佢同佢啲兄弟去兩日一夜澳門，<br />\n<br />\n我ok無問題亦無多問，<br />\n<br />\n但原來係同個個女仔去左澳門，<br />\n<br />\n我亦都知道佢依家已經無同個個女仔一齊了，<br />\n<br />\n但係最近佢公司有個女仔同佢表白，<br />\n<br />\n佢只係表明自己已經三十幾歳但係無表明過佢有女朋友，<br />\n<br />\n我唔知道我應該點做，如果係你，你會點處理？"},{"pid":"075f13dcea9fa79a64fdafd5a1d8988d45ac4b6e","tid":984553,"uid":107364,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T01:53:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6f09e1b1203d85dfcd33ad48b99d4d429ec0717a","tid":984553,"uid":146299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T01:56:58.000Z","msg":"仲問？你知答案的"},{"pid":"a37917cabb8b77993f83999ca0a05d68d4b9de58","tid":984553,"uid":39973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T01:57:31.000Z","msg":"其實你男朋友都真係好多女食WOR<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8772b5b374ae3dafc06597a4dcd88ba4b574f94","tid":984553,"uid":6675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T02:01:44.000Z","msg":"全世界得佢一個男人?? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98f10cb3ad6b081b41c2a89d368c89342f32ab07","tid":984553,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c